title: I didnt recieve rank icon FeelsBadMan
body: I don't know why I didn't receive it, so many people on my friends list already have theirs pls help! Thanks{{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}}

replies.body:
We can't roll these ranked rewards to everyone at the same time, so we're doing them over time. We're trying to get them all out by the end of the month, so sit tight until we can finish up distribution. We're not gonna leave you behind, friend.

Let me know if you have any questions.
